                  </persName>
             depos'd, that going to see the Deceased on her Death-bed, she told her that she was in bodily Health before the prisoner arrested her, and that he had been her Death; but that she freely forgave him, and hoped God would also. That she, this Deponent, heard the prisoner say to Hart, Ye old Bitch, will you rescue my Prisoner? and then struck her, Mrs. Hart, with a Key. 
               <persName id="t17211206-9-person91">
