             deposed that it was the Prisoner that bled and not the Deceas'd; that all the Evidences for the Deceas'd were scandalous Persons, and particularly, that Hart was a wicked abandon'd Wretch, and would swear any thing. The Jury considering the whole, <rs id="t17211206-9-verdict47" type="verdictDescription">
